Package org.eclipse.emf.compare.rcp.ui.internal.structuremergeviewer.groups

Class StructureMergeViewerGrouper

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.emf.compare.rcp.ui.internal.structuremergeviewer.groups.StructureMergeViewerGrouper
public final class StructureMergeViewerGrouper extends Object
This class will be used by the EMF Compare UI to group differences together in the structural differences tree viewer.

4.0
